'''''torech''''' is a [[Sindarin]] word glossed as "tunnel; hole, excavation",<ref name=UI>{{HM|UI}}, p. 490</ref> and "secret hole, lair".<ref name=PE17>{{PE|17}}, p. 188</ref>
==Etymology==
The word ''torech'' is a derivative of the [[Sundocarme|root]] TOR ("secrete, hide"). An associated word is [[Quenya]] ''[[ekka]]''.<ref name=PE17/>
